{
  "chapter": 27,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十七回·死亡游戏\n\n风四娘追问冰冰失踪原因，得知是轩辕三成下药、轩辕三缺带走冰冰送给了鲨王。鲨王徒弟鱼吃人对冰冰很客气，将她软禁。风四娘告诉萧十一郎，八仙船上的鲨王和所有请帖上有名字的人（除花如玉外）已全部被杀，用的是一刀毙命的快刀，萧十一郎被栽赃。\n\n风四娘道出此行的真正目的——连城璧约她月圆之夜在水月楼相见。沈璧君欲离去，被风四娘拦住。\n\n王猛突然闯入，说在水里捞到了史秋山的尸体，指控风四娘是凶手。霍无病也质问风四娘。萧十一郎出言解围，推理死者并非死在船上而是在水中被杀。他进一步质疑死者身份，认为可能有人假扮史秋山。沈璧君忽然一反沉默的常态，开口道破——死者就是史秋山。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_bing_bing",
      "text": "那天你怎么会忽然不见了的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我本来不能喝酒，回去时好像就有点醉，想喝杯茶解酒……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "他好像想利用我要挟萧……萧大哥做一件事。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "他软禁我的地方，萧十二郎当然知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "可是我却没有想到，他居然会带萧大哥来找我。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也想不到鲨王居然会有这么样一个徒弟。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他实在不能算是个好徒弟，却不知是不是个好朋友？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你虽然没有去过八仙船，我却去过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你见到了鲨王？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我见到了他，他却没有看见我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "因为死人是看不见别人的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "鲨王已死了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "不但鲨王死了，请帖上有名字的人，除了花如玉外，已全都死了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "是谁杀了他们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "本来应该是你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "是我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "至少别人都会认为是你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "杀他们的，是把快刀，而且只用了一刀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "除了萧十一郎外，还有谁能一刀杀了鲨王、鱼吃人？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "除了萧十一郎外，还有谁能一刀杀了轩辕三成？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你想不出？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你想得出？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我何必去想？这种事我遇见的反正不是第一次了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你们是怎么会来这里的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "为了一个约会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "别人的约会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "养狗的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "连城璧。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "就在这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "就在这水月楼？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "月圆之夜，水月楼。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "时候已不早了，我……我已该走了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你真的要走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我们虽然一起来的，可是你不必陪我走。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你要一个人走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "不行。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "为什么不行？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你连一杯酒都没有陪我喝，就想走了？打破头我也不会让你走的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你醉了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "不管我醉了没有，你都不能走。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你若一定要我喝，我就喝，可是喝完了我还是要走的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你要走，也得跟我一起走，我们既然是一起来的就得一起走。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "楼梯下的人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们两个谁都不许走。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_meng",
      "text": "刚才是你在下面鬼叫？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "哼。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_meng",
      "text": "你不许我走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "哼。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_meng",
      "text": "你知不知道我现在为什么还坐在这里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_meng",
      "text": "现在我还没有走，只因为我根本就不想走。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你想走也走不了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_meng",
      "text": "为什么走不了？难道你还想拉住我？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "哼。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_meng",
      "text": "只可惜腿是长在我自己身上的，我要走的时候，随便谁也拉不住。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "腿虽然长在你自己身上，可是你的左腿若要走，我就砍断你的左腿，右腿若要走我就砍断你的右腿。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_meng",
      "text": "若是我两条腿都要走，你就把我两条腿都砍下来？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "哼。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_meng",
      "text": "一个女人若是少了两条腿，岂非难看得很？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "那至少还比脸上多了个大洞的男人好看。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_meng",
      "text": "你脸上好像并没有大洞，连小洞都没有。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "那只因为我从来也没有跟你打过交道。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_meng",
      "text": "谁跟我打过交道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "史老二。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_meng",
      "text": "史秋山？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "难道你已忘了他？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_meng",
      "text": "难道他脸上已多了个大洞？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你为什么不自己下去看看？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_meng",
      "text": "你是哪里找到他的？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "在水里。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_meng",
      "text": "我本来还以为他忽然溜了，想不到……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你也想不到他已被人像死鱼般抛在水里？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_meng",
      "text": "我实在想不到。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你也不知道是谁杀了他？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你若不知道，还有谁知道？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "因为你就是凶手。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_meng",
      "text": "为什么我应该知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_wu_bing",
      "speaker_name": "霍无病",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你是不是早已认得史秋山？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_huo_wu_bing",
      "text": "我认得的人很多。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_wu_bing",
      "speaker_name": "霍无病",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "他是不是也早已认出了你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_wu_bing",
      "speaker_name": "霍无病",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "他刚才是不是一直都在跟着你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_wu_bing",
      "speaker_name": "霍无病",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "他既然一直在你身旁，若有别人来杀了他，你会不知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_huo_wu_bing",
      "text": "我说不知道，就是不知道。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_wu_bing",
      "speaker_name": "霍无病",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你知道什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_huo_wu_bing",
      "text": "我至少知道一件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_wu_bing",
      "speaker_name": "霍无病",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你说。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "世上绝没有任何人会不声不响的站在那里，让别人把自己的脸打出个大洞来，除非他是个木头人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "史秋山当然不是木头人，是江湖中惟一得到铁扇门真传的高手，若有人再做兵器谱，他的铁扇子至少可以排名在前三十位之内。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_wu_bing",
      "speaker_name": "霍无病",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你知道的事倒还不少。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我还知道，就算他是个木头人，若被人抛在水里，也会有'噗通'一声响的，这里的人都不聋，为什么没听见？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 383
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_wu_bing",
      "speaker_name": "霍无病",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你说为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为他根本不是死在这条船上的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_wu_bing",
      "speaker_name": "霍无病",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "若不是死在这条船上，死在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "水里。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "水里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_wang_meng",
      "text": "在水里杀人，就不会有声音发出来，所以船上的人才没有听见动静。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "他刚才明明还在船上，怎么会忽然到水里去了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_wang_meng",
      "text": "我刚才明明还在楼上，怎么会忽然下楼来了？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "是你自己下来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_wang_meng",
      "text": "我可以自己下楼，他为什么不能自己下水？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "他好好的在船上站着，为什么要自己下水？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_wang_meng",
      "text": "这一点我也想不通，我也正想去问问他。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "只可惜他已没法子告诉你。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_wang_meng",
      "text": "这个人的确已没法子告诉我，可是史秋山……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你看不出这个人就是史秋山？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_wang_meng",
      "text": "你看得出？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_wang_meng",
      "text": "你是凭哪点看出来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_wang_meng",
      "text": "史秋山忽然不见，你却在水里捞出了这么样一个人，所以你认为这个人就是史秋山，其实……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "其实怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_wang_meng",
      "text": "其实你自己现在一定也没有把握，能断定这个人就是史秋山。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 437
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_wu_bing",
      "speaker_name": "霍无病",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你是说史老二自己溜下水去，杀了这个人，再把这个扮成他的样子，让别人认为他已死了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_huo_wu_bing",
      "text": "这难道不可能？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_wu_bing",
      "speaker_name": "霍无病",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "他为什么要做这种事？为什么要连我们兄弟也瞒住？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_huo_wu_bing",
      "text": "这些你本该去问问他自己的，除了他自己之外，只怕谁也没法子答复。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 453
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_wu_bing",
      "speaker_name": "霍无病",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我还是有句话要问你。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_wu_bing",
      "speaker_name": "霍无病",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "这个人若不是史秋山，史秋山的人在哪里？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他的人就在这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就在这里。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个人就是史秋山。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    }
